      <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-6 bg-white/20 text-white backdrop-blur-sm">📍 Birmingham</p>
      <h1 class="font-display font-extrabold text-white leading-tight max-w-2xl">About the Barnt Green Cattery in Birmingham</h1>
      <p class="mt-5 text-white/80 text-lg max-w-xl leading-relaxed">A purpose-built countryside retreat, designed with your cat's comfort and happiness in mind.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Location section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-brand-bg">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold text-ink leading-tight">The perfect location for a cat hotel</h2>
          <p class="mt-5 text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">The Barnt Green Cattery is ideally located in the Birmingham countryside (close to Bromsgrove and Redditch), which gives our rural retreat complete privacy and security as well as being well away from the noisy city traffic.</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">The cattery is South facing so that in the winter months the bad weather is behind us and the summer sun brings warmth and brightness all day long to the front of the cattery, which overlooks a colourful garden and large pond.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="/P3221/images/about-cat1.jpg" alt="Barnt Green Cattery location" class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full object-cover" width="500" height="370" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Comfort section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-cream border-y border-border">
