        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
          <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold text-ink leading-tight">A cattery designed with your cat's comfort in mind</h2>
          <p class="mt-5 text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">Our boarding cattery has everything your cat needs to feel at home. We have large, comfy chalets with climbing frames, platforms and toys.</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">The centrally heated bedrooms, warm winter quarters and large exercise conservatory make it the ideal base to explore. Our cat hotel has a total of forty individual chalets all designed and built to the highest standards.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAB standard chalets -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-brand-bg">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold text-ink leading-tight">F.A.B standard chalets</h2>
          <p class="mt-5 text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">All our chalets are built to F.A.B standards to accommodate at least two cats and we have twelve extra large family units for up to four cats.</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">Our largest chalet, called the Penthouse, can accommodate up to eight cats. All cats staying at any of our chalets have to be from the same household.</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">The chalets are fully insulated and individually heated with thermostat control, so that even in very cold weather our guests are warm as toast.</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">The chalets are full height and beds and bedding are off the floor on low tables. A picture window overlooks the individual, outside covered runs which have climbing frames, platforms and shelving at different heights to provide three-dimensional space to climb and perch.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="/P3221/images/about-cat3.jpg" alt="FAB standard chalets at Barnt Green Cattery" class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full object-cover" width="500" height="370" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Year round boarding -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-cream border-y border-border">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
