        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-border text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">👪</div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-extrabold text-ink mb-3">12 Family Units</h3>
          <p class="text-ink-soft text-sm leading-relaxed">Extra large family units for up to four cats from the same household, with our Penthouse accommodating up to eight.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-border text-center">
